This is my first GG map so be nice :) I've just been hooked on GunGame lately, it's so awesome.. Anyways, people spawn behind the tower and the cover walls on the sides. The four bouldings on the sides have stairs down to two halls, having some wheels for cover (don't worry, they're static :P). The two staircases that go down the holes in the ground leads to a small labyrinth. There's windows (with bars) between the labyrinth section in the middle and the halls. I didn't care much for adding proper light sources, so you will just have to cope with this I haven't played this on any server, this is the first release so I don't know how well this will play.. Anyways, have fun :D NAV FILE UPLOADED TOMORROW

Hello all, this is my first ever map for any game ever. It is supposed to be a medieval dungeon with a Halloween theme, in a rats style. 
This was a really good learning experience! Hopefully the map itself still works fine, and people enjoy the all the little details I put in it. 

There are a  couple of different avenues you can take when playing this map. You can snipe from the top of the iron maidens, go over the table, under the table, or across the barrels over the chain.

All of the models and textures, for the most part, were created by me, which took forever. Other than the charple hanging in the cell and the leet/gign heads, there is no vanilla content in this map!

GoonSwarm Sandbox

|: author......electronaut <kabojnk@gmail.com> 
|: file...........gg_gswarm.bsp
|: map style..gun game
|: date.........October 30th, 2006


Author Comments:

I intended to make a small gun game map for a private server I like to play on with some friends.  The map was created with 32 spawn points, but only to keep it so players won't be stuck in spectator mode.

The skybox was a poor last-minute hack job.  Anyone who knows anything about mapping should see that the palm trees are horribly off-scale.  The FPS for the map should be pretty decent, however.  And the map is fairly symmetrical, so neither team should have issues dealing with disadvantages.

- E
